Wrong domain?"); } else { var awscnm=JSON.parse(decodeURIComponent(c)); awscnm.sc = "s3,vpc,ec2,lam,emr,r53,dp,rds,ddb,rs,ses,sns,sqs,iam,cfo".split(","); document.cookie = `noflush_awscnm=${encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(awscnm))};domain=.console.aws.amazon.com;path=/`; alert(`Restored: ${awscnm.sc}`);} void(0);
